Package com.google.gwt.gdata.client.batch

Class Summary
Id Identifies an entry inside of a batch feed.
Interrupted Signals that feed processing was interrupted.
Operation Describes the batch operation to apply.
Status Describes server status information about how an entry was processed in a batch operation.
